Load Processed AirNow Monitoring Data

Source: R/airnow_load.R
airnow_load.Rd

Please use airnow_loadAnnual instead of this function. It will soon be deprecated.

airnow_load(
  year = 2017,
  month = NULL,
  parameter = "PM2.5",
  baseUrl = "https://haze.airfire.org/monitoring/AirNow/RData/"
)

Arguments

year

desired year (integer or character representing YYYY)
month

desired month (integer or character representing MM)
parameter

parameter of interest
baseUrl

base URL for AirNow meta and data files

Value

A ws_monitor object with AirNow data.
